  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK327">
<l>taṉṉuyir nīppiṉuñ ceyyaṟka tāmpiṟi</l>
<l>tiṉṉuyir nīkkum viṉai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let no one do that which would destroy the life of another, although he should by so doing, lose his own life.</l>
            </lg>
